traits.name: Game Access
traits.description: This NFT is your key to Betwixt: The Story of You. Follow the link below to gain access: https://nft.betwixt.life/register

metadata.description:
Each NFT unlocks an app on your phone (available on iOS and Android) that gives you access to Betwixt: The Story of You. There are 11 quests dropping weekly at the same time for everyone, with dedicated chat rooms to connect with the team and other holders.

In addition, your NFT gets you:

 – an animation of your evolving work of art, plus a still image of its final manifestation;

 – behind-the-scenes access to extra resources such as self-reflection deep dives, guided meditations and other creative resiliency tools.
metadata.name: Triangulation - The path to self-discovery #1
